Zeba (zebashaikh_._ ) added our 1% Salicylic Acid Gel Face Wash, 2% Salicylic Acid Serum, and 10% Niacinamide Serum to her routine to fight her pesky acne.

Daytime Skincare Routine
✨ Wash your face with the 1% Salicylic Acid Gel Face Wash
✨ Apply 3-5 drops of 2% Salicylic Acid Serum on your skin and massage till completely absorbed

✨ Apply 3-5 drops of 10% Niacinamide Face serum and  massage into the skin in an upward motion
✨ Apply a moisturizer for nourishment
